categories: Category:Imperial Intelligence personnel of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: Jaxsinne Tamm was a female individual who served in the military intelligence of the Galactic Republic during the Clone Wars, holding the military rank of commander. When the Galactic Empire replaced the Republic, Tamm continued serving in intelligence, helping the Empire track down Jedi as part of Order 66 and the Great Jedi Purge. Eventually, Tamm defected and came to regret her actions.
